  "text": "The use of donor oocytes is the only treatment for women at risk of POI with good pregnancy outcome. Oocyte vitrification is method of fertility preservation against the ageing process. The robust results after the transplantation of the cryo-preserved ovarian tissue suggest that this method could be an alternative strategy for fertility preservation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
